&quot;But here's more that supports my position as the organization, at minimum, is presenting a &quot;religious&quot; front: In their Newcomer's corner, the navigation on the left-hand side include references to congregations, ministries, and a &quot;Church of Larger Fellowship&quot;.&quot;<br>
