The Church of the Larger Fellowship is not really a church.  They have no church meeting house.  It's for those UUs who live in an area where there is no concrete church to attend.  They send out publications, you can order curricula for the kids and yourself, they write most of the UU curricula as well.  It's a support link for those UUs who live in the bible belt or way mid west or those who move overseas, or those who don't like the make up the the concrete church near them.<br>
<br>
